  fhir:description [ fhir:v "This resource is used to record detailed information about a  diagnosis that has risen to a level of concern. The condition could be a point in time diagnosis in context of an encounter, it could be an item on the practitioner's Problem List, or it could be a concern that doesn't exist on the practitioner's Problem List."] ; # 
